In the steps below, compilation is not required.  You can simply use
the src/lru_cache.h file in your project directly; there are no object
files needed.  In order to run the unit tests and see it in action, do
the following:

_____________________
Installation from SVN

 $ make -f Makefile.cvs
 $ ./configure
 $ make

_________________________
Installation from tarball

 $ ./configure
 $ make
